<HEAD>Iran's Deputy Foreign Minister Resigns</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Javad Larijani, Iran's deputy foreign
minister for European and American affairs, has resigned, the
official Islamic Republic News Agency reported.
   The agency said Larijani was replaced by Mahmoud Vaezi, the
Foreign Ministry's European director. It gave no reason for
